  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "文部科学省（MEXT）によって承認された日本漢字能力検定の問題が7,000問収録されています（2002年6月まで）。プレイヤーは自分のレベルに合わせて12段階の問題から選んで学習することができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The third installment of \"Kanji BOY\" that makes you smarter while playing games. The number of questions recorded is over 7,000! As you play, you will naturally acquire kanji. There are two game modes. There is a \"existing question collection mode\" where you can play the exams from the 2nd to 10th grades that have been asked in the past, and a \"mini game mode\" where you can get idioms about your body, health, animals, and living.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
